  "title": "beautician",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Engage &amp; Inspire Customers:</strong> Actively engage with customers by demonstrating high-quality skincare products and showcasing their benefits to create a memorable shopping experience.</li>\n  <li><strong>Provide Expert Guidance:</strong> Assist customers in selecting the perfect products and services tailored to their individual needs, ensuring they leave satisfied with their purchases.</li>\n  <li><strong>Build Relationships:</strong> Cultivate lasting relationships with new and existing customers by offering exceptional service and personalized recommendations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Achieve Team Goals:</strong> Collaborate with your team to meet and exceed store targets, while contributing to a positive and motivating work atmosphere.</li>\n  <li><strong>Ensure Smooth Operations:</strong> Manage day-to-day activities in the store, maintaining high standards of customer service and store presentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Benefits:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Attractive Compensation:</strong> Competitive base salary with uncapped commission opportunities, allowing you to earn a high income based on performance.</li>\n  <li><strong>Dynamic Work Culture:</strong> Enjoy a friendly, fun, and inclusive working environment where teamwork and personal growth are valued.</li>\n  <li><strong>Employee Perks:</strong> Access exclusive staff discounts on products and collections.</li>\n  <li><strong>Convenient Location:</strong> Work in a prime location, just steps away from the MRT station, for easy commuting.</li>\n</ul>",
